{"tid":1442335,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣組麻煩入來！］善用敵人hashtag攻佔淺藍，以彼之道，還施彼身","createTime":"2019-08-11T02:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:50:03.000Z","uid":300447,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a83ea80dd87006721ecdaa3887897b1da103da73","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:31:47.000Z","msg":"建制派最近常用 #守護香港 #全民撐警 的 hashtag。<br />\n<br />\n大家麻煩記住，hashtag是可以用來search！！！<br />\n<br />\n就是說，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果我們在面向淺藍的文宣中加入 #守護香港的hashtag，同時用其他hashtag</span></span></strong> 如：<br />\n#支持成立獨立調查委員會 <br />\n#官員問責 <br />\n#政府出賣警隊 <br />\n<br />\n藍絲們很有可能在search #守護香港時多接觸到我們的文宣！<br />\n<br />\n從心理學角度而言，當年佔中時建制派最喜歡的把「反佔中」與「保民生」結合，引起聯想，現在我們絕對有能力<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以彼之道，還施彼身</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n文宣的兄弟姐妹們，拜託，讓我們搶奪守護香港之名，推而廣之，把所有聽起來中立，而建制派喜歡用的hashtag或者是口號都放在我們的文宣裡，搶佔中立地帶的發言權！"},{"pid":"16924f72a2cc91df0f7bbe72e7cef348aeb9abe1","tid":1442335,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:33:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02db8e42f78e83d4469cd556a067811672be9861","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:34:18.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"bb5f7d6300c666e80c23785e506d0b996517f379","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:34:34.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"c59fb9384967df5cf744edab8614dd513279d5e5","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"d82bee5b57d9967ceb1452ac5dec1a1fd1908e69","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:34:56.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"bd06d5b7cd85d57b5ed87c2fdbd758aaaa1c43ba","tid":1442335,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:35:00.000Z","msg":"唔係唔得<br />\n但真係有人係fb禁個hash tag黎睇架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nig又少藍絲用"},{"pid":"1fbe828c08cc4cdf57a1243ded4c4b95ee34d1d8","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:35:07.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"183de1dce592677095daa8bffa6f5d14a7d0a94a","tid":1442335,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02db8e42f78e83d4469cd556a067811672be9861","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:34:18.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:36:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3f38ce14237fbbffde7b9c56aa22070958a4b751","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd06d5b7cd85d57b5ed87c2fdbd758aaaa1c43ba","tid":1442335,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:35:00.000Z","msg":"唔係唔得<br />\n但真係有人係fb禁個hash tag黎睇架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nig又少藍絲用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:41:39.000Z","msg":"另一好處是我們向淺藍家人親友whatsapp 轉文宣時可以一個package把那些只談經濟的中立長輩圖及有政治成分的混在一起，潛移默化。<br />\n<br />\n他們見到有守護香港，立即稍微放下心裡戒備。最近身邊朋友都說自己不管send什麼比家人，對方都assume是黃色文宣而已讀不回，我們要做的是搶佔所謂中立派的地位，扮成中立甚至用類似建制的口號，讓他們混亂，讓他們願意看我們的文宣。他們不接受，就問他們是否不願意守護香港"},{"pid":"123acd2699b8f5b8454b4c7228077a6d8fe5aeed","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:42:23.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"60205e78f393678f6a7465d9c8bb3dbd2ece1334","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:42:33.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"116df1dc1a5e173bfa56ef3e36d7e4a113f2b295","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"174bf8a814e71782e04acbc3c58536d3a738e792","tid":1442335,"uid":51499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2b9646095063544ea2c82eed2572722289745bac","tid":1442335,"uid":51499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:43:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a2a1d24b26485796923dc00fd0c7bafc5ff24406","tid":1442335,"uid":110332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:52:40.000Z","msg":"有什麼是抗爭者可做，但還未做的事？X先生說：「第一，我講多次，就係日日打721呢個死穴，因為林鄭同警方依家完全冇得拆。第二，將民建聯同黑警綑綁，要佢哋永不分離。中央撐警，建制派一定要歸隊，冇可能割席。好多人冇留意到北京撐警，其實係一把雙刃劍，好處係穩定軍心，防止警察叛變，壞處係會累死建制派。大家點解唔日日問吓民建聯啲區議員同立法會議員，『你撐唔撐警』、『覺唔覺得警察濫用暴力』呢？記住問是非題，一係yes，一係no，咪畀位佢遊花園呀。」<br />\n<br />\nBy 政界猛人揭林鄭底牌 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d9b01ef538cba1196acf1f9955bce1ed626d6b1d","tid":1442335,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b85cbf94daee4f6f78df009a9517de015f68a74c","tid":1442335,"uid":300447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:42:36.000Z","msg":"大家在fb ig share post 都不斷加入 #守護香港 ，行動！！！"},{"pid":"b22c52a6d4b6ffada939b1cc017594f824d14f19","tid":1442335,"uid":56092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:50:03.000Z","msg":"push"}]}